skill.name: Orb of Deception
skill.description: Ahri fires an orb in a line dealing magic damage to enemies it passes through. It then returns to her, dealing true damage to all enemies it passes through.
skill.description_es: Ahri lanza un orbe en linea que inflige 175 de daño mágico a todos los enemigos que atraviesa de ida, y 175 de daño verdadero a los que atraviesa de vuelta.
skill.description_pt: Ahri dispara um orbe em linha reta causando dano mágico aos inimigos acertados. O orbe então retorna a ela causando dano verdadeiro a todos os acertados
skill.description_de: Ahri schleudert eine Kugel geradlinig nach vorne und fügt allen getroffenen Gegnern  magischen Schaden zu. Die Kugel kehrt dann zu ihr zurück und fügt allen getroffenen Gegnern absoluten Schaden zu.
skill.description_ru: Ари выпускает шар в линию, нанося магический урон врагам, через которых проходит. Затем он возвращается к ней, нанося чистый урон всем врагам, через которых проходит.
skill.description_ch: Ahri fires an orb in a line dealing magic damage to enemies it passes through. It then returns to her, dealing true damage to all enemies it passes through.
skill.description_tr: Ahri içinden geçen düşmanlara büyü hasarı veren, çizgi halinde giden bir küre fırlatır. Daha sonra küre ona dönerken içinden geçtiği bütün düşmanlara gerçek hasar verir.
skill.description_vi: Ahri bắn ra quả cầu ma thuật theo đường thẳng, gây sát thương phép lên tất cả kẻ địch nó lướt qua và gây sát thương chuẩn lên tất cả kẻ địch trên đường trở lại
skill.description_fr: Ahri lance un orbe en ligne droite infligeant des dégâts magiques à tous les ennemis qu\'il traverse.L\'orbe revient ensuite à elle, infligeant des dégâts bruts à tous les ennemis qu\'il traverse.
skill.description_pl: Ahri wystrzeliwuje poruszającą się wzdłuż linii prostej kulę, zadającą 175/250/400 obrażeń magicznych wszystkim wrogom, przez których przeniknie. Następnie kula wraca do Ahri, zadając 150/225/400 nieuchronnych obrażeń wszystkim wrogom, przez których przeniknie.
skill.description_it: Ahri fires an orb in a line dealing magic damage to enemies it passes through. It then returns to her, dealing true damage to all enemies it passes through.

skill.name: Galaxy Shield-Blast
skill.description: Annie blasts a cone of fire dealing magic damage to enemies in front of her, then shields herself for 4 seconds.
skill.description_es: Annie irradia un cono de fuego que inflige 150 de daño mágico a los enemigos frente a ella, luego crea un escudo de 225 de vida durante 4 seg.
skill.description_pt: Annie dispara fogo em formato de cone causando dano mágico aos inimigos em sua frente, em seguida, consegue um escudo por 4 segundos
skill.description_de: Annie wirft einen flammenden Feuerkegel, der Gegnern vor ihr magischen Schaden zufügt. Dann erhält sie 4 Sekunden lang einen Schild, der Schaden absorbiert.
skill.description_ru: Энни взрывает огненный конус, нанося магический урон врагам перед собой, затем укрывается на 4 секунды.
skill.description_ch: Annie blasts a cone of fire dealing magic damage to enemies in front of her, then shields herself for 4 seconds.
skill.description_tr: Annie önündeki düşmanlara büyü hasarı veren bir ateş konisi patlatır,sonra kendisini 4 saniye koruyan bir kalkan kazanır.
skill.description_vi: Annie chưởng lửa theo hình nón, gây sát thương phép, sau đó tạo lá chắn và hấp thụ sát thương trong 4s.
skill.description_fr: Annie projette des flammes dans une zone conique, infligeant des dégâts magiques aux ennemis devant elle, puis s\'entoure d\'un bouclier pendant 4 secondes.
skill.description_pl: Annie osłania się tarczą o wartości 150% obrażeń i na obszarze stożka razi wrogów ogniem, zadając im 150/200/300 obrażeń magicznych.
skill.description_it: Annie blasts a cone of fire dealing magic damage to enemies in front of her, then shields herself for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Enchanted Crystal Arrow
skill.description: Ashe fires an arrow toward the farthest enemy that explodes on the first target hit, dealing magic damage to all nearby enemies and stunning them.
skill.description_es: Ashe dispara una flecha al enemigo más lejano, la cual explotará al impactar a su primer objetivo e infligirá 250 de daño mágico a todos los enemigos cercanos y los aturdirá durante 2 seg.
skill.description_pt: Ashe dispara uma flecha em direção ao inimigo mais distante, que explode no primeiro acerto, causando dano mágico a todos os inimigos próximos e atordoando-os
skill.description_de: Ashe feuert einen Pfeil auf den am weitesten entfernten Gegner, der beim ersten getroffenen Ziel explodiert. Dadurch erleiden alle Gegner in der Nähe magischen Schaden und werden Sekunden lang betäubt.
skill.description_ru: Эш стреляет и стреляет в самого дальнего врага, который взрывается при первом попадании в цель, нанося магический урон всем находящимся поблизости противникам и оглушая их.
skill.description_ch: Ashe fires an arrow toward the farthest enemy that explodes on the first target hit, dealing magic damage to all nearby enemies and stunning them.
skill.description_tr: Ashe ilk çarptığı hedefte patlayan en uzak düşmana doğru bir ok atar, çarptığı hedefin yakınındaki düşmanlara büyü hasarı verir ve onları sersemletir.
skill.description_vi: Ashe bắn ra một mũi tên khổng lồ về phía kẻ địch xa nhất, mũi tên phát nổ khi chạm vào mục tiêu đầu tiên trúng phải, gây sát thương phép lên tất cả kẻ địch cạnh bên và làm choáng chúng.
skill.description_fr: Ashe lance une flèche de glace vers l\'ennemi le plus loin, touchant le premier adversaire touché. Elle lui inflige des dégâts et l\'étourdit en fonction du nombre de cases parcourues.
skill.description_pl: Ashe wystrzeliwuje strzałę w kierunku najbardziej oddalonego wroga. Po zderzeniu się z pierwszym trafionym wrogiem strzała ogłusza go na 1,2/2/2,5 sekundy i zadaje obrażenia o wartości 250/350/700. Ogłuszenie trwa tym dłużej, im dalej przeleci strzała.
skill.description_it: Ashe fires an arrow toward the farthest enemy that explodes on the first target hit, dealing magic damage to all nearby enemies and stunning them.

skill.name: Mobilize the Fleet
skill.description: Aurelion Sol launches fighters, which fly out to random enemies, deal magic damage, drain mana, and then return. Aurelion Sol initially launches 4 fighters plus 2 additional ones on subsequent casts. Fighters prefer to target nearby enemies.
skill.description_es: Aurelion Sol lanza sus cazas, los cuales vuelan hacia enemigos aleatorios, infligen 120 de daño mágico y luego regresan. Aurelion Sol lanza a todos los cazas disponibles más 3 adicionales al utilizar este hechizo. Los cazas priorizan atacar a enemigos cercanos.
skill.description_pt: Aurelion Sol lança lutadores, que pulam em direção a inimigos aleatórios, causam dano mágico e então retornam. Aurelion Sol lança todos o lutadores prontos e depois mais 3 adicionais. Os lutadores priorizam atingir inimigos próximos
skill.description_de: Aurelion Sol feuert Kampfflieger ab, die zufällige Gegner ansteuern, ihnen magischen Schaden zufügen und dann zu ihm zurückkehren. Bei Aktivierung seiner Fähigkeit feuert Aurelion Sol alle bereiten Kampfflieger sowie 3 zusätzliche ab. Die Kämpfer visieren vorrangig nahe Gegner an.
skill.description_ru: ауриен сол запускает истребителей, которые вылетают случайным врагам, наносят магический урон, а затем возвращаются. ауриен сол запускает всех готовых бойцов плюс 3 дополнительных, когда он кастует. Бойцы предпочитают атаковать ближайших врагов.
skill.description_ch: Aurelion Sol launches fighters, which fly out to random enemies, deal magic damage, and then return. Aurelion Sol launches all ready fighters plus 3 additional when he casts. Fighters prefer to target nearby enemies.
skill.description_tr: Aurelion Sol rastgele düşmanlara uçan, büyü hasarı veren ve sonra ona geri dönen savaşçılar çıkarır. Aurelion Sol\'ün savaşçıları varsa manası dolduğunda ek 3 savaşçı daha çıkarır. Savaşçılar yakındaki düşmanları hedef alır.
skill.description_vi: Aurelion Sol triển khai máy bay tiêm kích tấn công các kẻ địch ngẫu nhiên, gây sát thương phép và quay trở về. Aurelion Sol sẽ tung tất cả những máy bay tiêm kích đã sẵn sàng cộng thêm 3 máy bay mỗi lần sử dụng kĩ năng. Máy bay tiêm kích ưu tiên nhắm đến kẻ địch xung quanh.
skill.description_fr: Aurelion Sol lance des drones qui volent vers des ennemis aléatoires, leur infligeant des dégâts avant de revenir vers lui. Ils attaquent en priorité les ennemis proches.
skill.description_pl: Aurelion Sol wysyła wojowników, którzy podlatują do losowych wrogów, zadając im 100/150/750 obrażeń magicznych, a następnie wracają. Aurelion Sol wysyła wszystkich gotowych wojowników oraz trzech dodatkowych przy rzuceniu zaklęcia. Wojownicy za cel obierają głównie pobliskich wrogów.
skill.description_it: Aurelion Sol launches fighters, which fly out to random enemies, deal magic damage, and then return. Aurelion Sol launches all ready fighters plus 3 additional when he casts. Fighters prefer to target nearby enemies.

skill.name: Rocket Grab
skill.description: Blitzcrank pulls the furthest enemy to him, dealing magic damage and stunning them for 2.5 seconds. The next attack after pulling knocks up for 1 second. Allies within range will prioritize attacking Blitzcrank\'s target.
skill.description_es: Blitzcrank atrae al enemigo más lejano hacia él, lo que inflige 250 de daño mágico y lo ayrde durante 2.5 seg. Susiguente ataque lo lanza por el aire durante 1 seg. Los aliados dentro del alcance preferirán atacar al objetivo de Blitzcrank.
skill.description_pt: Blitzcrank puxa o inimigo mais distante até ele, causando dano mágico e atordoando-o por 2.5 segundos. O primeiro ataque depois do puxão é dado em 1 segundo. Aliados próximos priorizarão atacar o alvo de Blitzcrank
skill.description_de: Blitzcrank zieht den am weitesten entfernten Gegner zu sich, fügt ihm magischen Schaden zu und betäubt ihn 2,5 Sekunden lang. Sein nächster Angriff nach dem Heranziehen schleudert das Ziel 1 Sekunde lang in die Luft. Verbündete in Reichweite priorisieren Angriffe auf Blitzcranks Ziel.
skill.description_ru: Блицкрэнк притягивает к себе самого дальнего врага, нанося магический урон и оглушая его на 2,5 секунды. Следующая атака после подтягивания выбивает на 1 секунду. Союзники в пределах досягаемости будут определять приоритет атакующей цели Блицкрэнка.
skill.description_ch: Blitzcrank pulls the furthest enemy to him, dealing magic damage and stunning them for 2.5 seconds. The next attack after pulling knocks up for 1 second. Allies within range will prioritize attacking Blitzcrank\'s target.
skill.description_tr: Blitzcrank ona en uzak düşmanı çeker, büyü hasarı verir ve 2.5 saniye boyunca sersemletir. Çektikten sonraki saldırısı 1 saniye boyunca havaya kaldırır. Menzil içindeki müttefikler Blitzcrank\'in hedefine saldırmaya öncelik verir.
skill.description_vi: Blitzcrank kéo kẻ địch xa nhất về phía mình, gây sát thương phép và làm choáng chúng. Đòn đánh tiếp theo sau khi kéo sẽ hất tung mục tiêu trong 1 giây.Đồng minh trong tầm sẽ ưu tiên tấn công mục tiêu của Blitzcrank.
skill.description_fr: Blitzcrank attire l\'ennemi le plus éloigné de lui, l\'étourdissant pendant quelques secondes et lui infligeant des dégâts. Sa prochaine attaque propulse l\'adversaire en l\'air.
skill.description_pl: Blitzcrank przyciąga najbardziej oddalonego od siebie przeciwnika, zadając mu 250/400/900 obrażeń magicznych i ogłuszając go na 2,5 sekundy. Następny atak po przyciągnięciu podrzuci cel na 1 sekundę. Sojusznicy w zasięgu będą priorytetyzować atakowanie celu Blitzcranka.
skill.description_it: Blitzcrank pulls the furthest enemy to him, dealing magic damage and stunning them for 2.5 seconds. The next attack after pulling knocks up for 1 second. Allies within range will prioritize attacking Blitzcrank\'s target.

skill.name: Ace in the Hole
skill.description: Caitlyn takes aim at the furthest enemy, firing a deadly bullet towards them that deals magic damage to the first enemy it hits.
skill.description_es: Caitlyn apunta al enemigo más lejano y dispara una bala letal que inflige 700 de daño mágico al primer enemigo que impacte.
skill.description_pt: Caitlyn mira no inimigo mais distante, disparando um tiro que causa dano mágico ao primeiro inimigo acertado
skill.description_de: Caitlyn nimmt den am weitesten entfernten Gegner ins Visier und feuert einen Schuss ab, der dem ersten getroffenen Gegner magischen Schaden zufügt.
skill.description_ru: Caitlyn takes aim at the furthest enemy, firing a deadly bullet towards them that deals magic damage to the first enemy it hits.
skill.description_ch: Caitlyn takes aim at the furthest enemy, firing a deadly bullet towards them that deals magic damage to the first enemy it hits.
skill.description_tr: Caitlyn, en uzaktaki düşmana nişan alır ve vurduğu ilk düşmana büyü hasarı veren ölümcül bir kurşun fırlatır.
skill.description_vi: Caitlyn nhắm bắn kẻ địch xa nhất, sau đó bắn ra một viên đạn chết chóc về phía mục tiêu gây sát thương phép lên mục tiêu đầu tiên trúng phải.
skill.description_fr: Caitlyn vise l\'ennemi le plus éloigné et tire une balle dévastatrice qui inflige des dégâts magiques au premier ennemi touché.
skill.description_pl: Caitlyn celuje w najdalszego wroga, a następnie wystrzeliwuje w jego kierunku zabójczy pocisk, który zadaje 700/1000/1800 obrażeń magicznych pierwszemu wrogowi, którego trafi.
skill.description_it: Caitlyn takes aim at the furthest enemy, firing a deadly bullet towards them that deals magic damage to the first enemy it hits.

skill.name: Rupture
skill.description: Cho\'Gath ruptures a large area, dealing magic damage and knocking up all enemies within.
skill.description_es: Cho\'Gath crea una ruptura en un área amplia, lo que inflige 150 de daño mágico y lanza por el aire a todos los enemigos dentro de ella durante 2 seg.
skill.description_pt: Cho\'Gath rompe uma grande área, causando dano mágico e batendo em todos os inimigos acertados
skill.description_de: Cho\'Gath lässt einen großen Bereich aufbrechen, verursacht magischen Schaden und schleudert alle Gegner im Gebie in die Luft.
skill.description_ru: Чо\'Гат разрывает большую область, нанося магический урон и подбрасывая всех врагов внутри.
skill.description_ch: Cho\'Gath ruptures a large area, dealing magic damage and knocking up all enemies within.
skill.description_tr: Cho\'Gath geniş bir alanı parçalayarak büyü hasarı verir ve içindeki tüm düşmanları havaya kaldırır.
skill.description_vi: Cho\'Gath làm rạn nứt một vùng rộng lớn, gây sát thương phép và hất tung tất cả kẻ địch trong vùng.
skill.description_fr: Cho\'Gath brise une zone étendue, infligeant des dégâts et projetant en l\'air les ennemis à l\'intérieur.
skill.description_pl: Cho’Gath rozrywa duży obszar, podrzucając znajdujących się na nim wrogów na 2/2/4 sekundy i zadając im 150/250/2000 obrażeń.
skill.description_it: Cho\'Gath ruptures a large area, dealing magic damage and knocking up all enemies within.

skill.name: Dreadnova Guillotine
skill.description: Darius dunks an enemy, dealing magic damage. If this kills the target, Darius immediately casts again. Targets below 50% health take double damage.
skill.description_es: Darius clava a un enemigo e inflige 400 de daño mágico. Si esto mata al objetivo, Darius volverá a lanzar este hechizo de inmediato. Los objetivos con menos del 50% de Vida reciben el doble de daño.
skill.description_pt: Darius corta um inimigo, causando dano mágico. Se o inimigo morrer, Darius imediatamente ataca denovo. Alvos abaixo de 50% da vida sofrem o dobro de dano
skill.description_de: Darius schlägt einen Gegner und fügt ihm magischen Schaden zu. Falls er das Ziel tötet, aktiviert Darius die Fähigkeit sofort ein zweites Mal. Ziele unter 50% Leben erleiden doppelten Schaden.
skill.description_ru: Дарий данкает врага, нанося магический урон. Если это убивает цель, Дарий сразу же делает следующее заклинание. Цели ниже 50% здоровья получают двойной урон.
skill.description_ch: Darius dunks an enemy, dealing magic damage. If this kills the target, Darius immediately casts again. Targets below 50% health take double damage.
skill.description_tr: Darius bir düşmana smaç basarak büyü hasarı verir. Eğer hedefi öldürürse, Darius hemen tekrar smaç basar. % 50 sağlığın altındaki hedefler iki kat hasar alır.
skill.description_vi: Darius bổ rìu một kẻ địch, gây sát thương phép. Nếu kĩ năng này hạ gục mục tiêu, Darius ngay lập tức sử dụng nó một lần nữa. Mục tiêu dưới 50% máu nhận gấp đôi sát thương.
skill.description_fr: Darius abat sa hache sur un ennemi, lui infligeant des dégâts. Si la cible meurt, Darius relance son sort immédiatement. Les dégâts sont doublés contre les adversaires qui ont moins de 50% de PV.
skill.description_pl: Darius rzuca wroga, zadając mu 400/500/750 obrażeń magicznych. Jeśli Darius w ten sposób zabije cel, natychmiastowo ponownie rzuca zaklęcie. Cele mające poniżej 50% zdrowia otrzymują podwójne obrażenia.
skill.description_it: Darius dunks an enemy, dealing magic damage. If this kills the target, Darius immediately casts again. Targets below 50% health take double damage.

skill.name: Chronobreak
skill.description: Ekko shatters the timeline, freezing all units in time before attacking enemies with bonus magic damage, applying on-hit effects, and reducing Attack Speed by 50% for 7 seconds. Ekko cannot die while he has stopped time.
skill.description_es: Ekko rompe el flujo temporal, lo que congela en el tiempo a todas las unidades y ataca a cada enemigo por 250 de daño mágico adicional y aplica efectos al impacto. Ekko no puede morir mientras esta en el tiempo está congelado.
skill.description_pt: Ekko interfere na linha do tempo, congelando todas as unidades no tempo, atacando cada inimigo com dano mágico bônus e aplicando efeitos ao acertá-los. Ekko não pode morrer enquanto o tempo estiver parado
skill.description_de: Ekko zerbricht die Zeitlinie und lässt alle Einheiten erstarren. Dann greift er an, fügt jedem Gegner zusätzlichen magischen Schaden zu und löst Treffereffekte aus. Während Ekko die Zeit anhält, kann er nicht sterben.
skill.description_ru: Экко разрушает временную шкалу, замораживая все юниты во времени, прежде чем атаковать каждого врага с бонусным магическим уроном и применяя эффекты при попадании. Экко не может умереть, пока он остановил время.
skill.description_ch: Ekko shatters the timeline, freezing all units in time before attacking each enemy with bonus magic damage and applying on-hit effects. Ekko cannot die while he has stopped time.
skill.description_tr: Ekko zaman çizgisini parçalar, saldırmadan önce bütün birimleri dondurur ve her bir düşmana ekstra büyü hasarı verir.Ekko zamanı durdururken ölemez.
skill.description_vi: Ekko phá hủy dòng thời gian, ngưng đọng tất cả trước khi tấn công chúng, gây thêm sát thương phép và áp dụng hiệu ứng đòn đánh. Ekko không thể bị hạ gục khi dừng thời gian.
skill.description_fr: Ekko arrête le temps, immobilisant toutes les unités avant d\'attaquer chaque ennemi. Il leur inflige des dégâts magiques bonus.
skill.description_pl: Ekko roztrzaskuje strumień czasu, zamrażając w nim wszystkie jednostki, a następnie atakuje każdego wroga, zadając 200/450/2000 bonusowych obrażeń magicznych i nakładając efekty przy trafieniu.
skill.description_it: Ekko shatters the timeline, freezing all units in time before attacking each enemy with bonus magic damage and applying on-hit effects. Ekko cannot die while he has stopped time.

skill.name: E.M.P.
skill.description: Ezreal fires an electromagnetic pulse at a random enemy that explodes on impact, dealing magic damage to all nearby enemies and increases the cost of their next spell cast by 40%.
skill.description_es: Ezreal lanza un pulso electromagnético a un enemigo aleatorio que explotará al hacer impacto, lo que inflige 250 de daño mágico a todos los enemigos cercanos e incrementará un 40% el costo de su siguente hechizo.
skill.description_pt: Ezreal dispara uma onda eletromagnética em um inimigo aleatório explodindo no impacto e causando dano mágico a todos os inimigos próximos e acrescentando o custo do próximo feitiço lançado de cada um em 40%
skill.description_de: Ezreal beschießt einen zufälligen Gegner mit einem elektromagnetischen Puls, der bei Kontakt explodiert, allen Gegnern in der Nähe Schaden zufügt und die Aktivierungskosten für ihre nächste Fähigkeit um 40% erhöht.
skill.description_ru: Эзреаль запускает электромагнитный импульс по случайному противнику, который взрывается при ударе, нанося магический урон всем находящимся поблизости противникам и увеличивает стоимость их следующего заклинания на 40%.
skill.description_ch: Ezreal fires an electromagnetic pulse at a random enemy that explodes on impact, dealing magic damage to all nearby enemies and increases the cost of their next spell cast by 40%.
skill.description_tr: Ezreal rastgele bir düşmana elektromanyetik bir darbe fırlatır, bu da çarptığında patlar, yakındaki tüm düşmanlara büyü hasarı verir ve bir sonraki büyü maliyetini% 40 artırır.
skill.description_vi: Ezreal bắn ra một quả cầu điện từ về phía một mục tiêu ngẫu nhiên. Quả cầu phát nổ khi va chạm, gây sát thương lên tất cả mục tiêu xung quanh vụ nổ và tăng năng 40% năng lượng tiêu hao của kĩ năng tiếp theo chúng thi triển.
skill.description_fr: Ezreal tire une impulsion électromagnétique sur un ennemi aléatoire. Il lui inflgie des dégâts ainsi qu\'aux ennemis proches et augmente le coût en mana de leur prochain sort.
skill.description_pl: Ezreal wystrzeliwuje w losowego wroga impuls elektromagnetyczny, który wybucha przy trafieniu, zadając 100/125/400 obrażeń magicznych wszystkim pobliskim wrogom i zwiększając koszt rzucenia przez nich następnego zaklęcia o 40%.
skill.description_it: Ezreal fires an electromagnetic pulse at a random enemy that explodes on impact, dealing magic damage to all nearby enemies and increases the cost of their next spell cast by 40%.

skill.name: Riposte
skill.description: Fiora enters a defensive stance for 1.5 seconds, becoming immune to damage and enemy spell effects. As she exits this stance, she ripostes, dealing magic damage to a nearby enemy and stunning them.
skill.description_es: Fiora adopta una posición defensiva durante .15 seg. lo cual la vuelve inmune al daño y los efectos de hechizos enemigos. Tras dejar esta posición, realiza una estocada que inflige 300 de daño mágico un enemigo cercano y lo aturde.
skill.description_pt: Fiora entra em posição defensiva por 1.5 segundos, se tornando imune a dano e efeitos de feitiços inimigos. Ao sair desse estado, ela contra-ataca causando dano mágico a inimigos próximos e os atordoando.
skill.description_de: Fiora nimmt 1,5 Sekunden lang eine defensive Haltung ein und wird immun gegen Schaden und gegnerische Fähigkeitseffekte. Beim Verlassen dieser Haltung kontert sie, fügt einem nahen Gegner magischen Schaden zu und betäubt ihn.
skill.description_ru: Фиора входит в защитную стойку на 1,5 секунды, становясь невосприимчивым к урону и эффектам заклинаний противника. Выходя из этой позиции, она наносит магический урон ближайшему врагу и оглушает его.
skill.description_ch: Fiora enters a defensive stance for 1.5 seconds, becoming immune to damage and enemy spell effects. As she exits this stance, she ripostes, dealing magic damage to a nearby enemy and stunning them.
skill.description_tr: Fiora, 1,5 saniyeliğine savunma duruşuna girerek hasara ve düşman büyü etkilerine karşı bağışıklık kazanır. Bu duruştan çıkarken, yakındaki bir düşmana büyü hasarı vererek boyunca onu sersemletir.
skill.description_vi: Fiora bước vào thế thủ trong 1.5 giây, trở nên miễn nhiễm với sát thương và hiệu ứng kĩ năng của đối thủ. Sau khi hết thời gian thủ thế, cô tung phản đòn, gây sát thương phép lên một mục tiêu cạnh bên và làm choáng chúng.
skill.description_fr: Fiora devient immunisée pendant 1,5 seconde, puis inflige des dégâts et étourdit l\'adversaire le plus proche.
skill.description_pl: Fiora wchodzi w defensywny stan na 1,5 sekundy, stając się niewrażliwa na obrażenia i efekty zaklęć wroga. Po wyjściu z tego stanu odpiera atak, zadając obrażeń magicznych i ogłuszając pobliskich wrogów.
skill.description_it: Fiora enters a defensive stance for 1.5 seconds, becoming immune to damage and enemy spell effects. As she exits this stance, she ripostes, dealing magic damage to a nearby enemy and stunning them.

skill.name: Chum the Waters
skill.description: Fizz throws a lure that attracts a shark, causing it to emerge after a brief delay. It deals magic damage to enemies caught, knocking them back and stunning them for 1.5 seconds.
skill.description_es: Fizz lanza un señuelo que atrae a un tiburón. Inflige 350 de daño mágico a los enemigos alcanzados y los lanza hacia atrás, lo que los aturde  durante 1.5 seg.
skill.description_pt: Fizz joga uma isca que atrai um tubarão, fazendo-o emergir depois de um curto tempo. Isso causa dano mágico aos inimigos pêgos, acertando-os e os atordoando por 1.5 segundos
skill.description_de: Fizz wirft einen Köder aus und lockt damit einen Hai an, der nach einer kurzen Verzögerung auftaucht. Gegner, die vom Hai erwischt werden, erleiden magischen Schaden, werden zurückgestoßen und 1,5 Sekunden lang betäubt.
skill.description_ru: Физз бросает приманку, которая привлекает акулу, заставляя ее появиться после короткой задержки. Наносит магический урон пойманным врагам, отбрасывая их назад и оглушая их на 1,5 секунды.
skill.description_ch: Fizz throws a lure that attracts a shark, causing it to emerge after a brief delay. It deals magic damage to enemies caught, knocking them back and stunning them for 1.5 seconds.
skill.description_tr: Fizz, bir köpekbalığını çeken ve kısa bir gecikmeden sonra ortaya çıkmasına neden olan bir yem fırlatır. Yakalanan düşmanlara büyü hasarı verir, onları havaya kaldırır ve 1,5 saniye boyunca sersemletir.
skill.description_vi: Fizz ném mồi câu để dụ cá mập trồi lên gây sát thương phép lên những kẻ địch bị cắn trúng, đồng thời hất văng và làm choáng chúng trong 1.5 giây.
skill.description_fr: Fizz lance un appât qui attire un requin et le fait surgir du sol, infligeant des dégâts et étourdissant les ennemis touchés.
skill.description_pl: Fizz rzuca przynętę wabiącą rekiny, które pojawiają się po krótkiej chwili. Zadaje 350/500/2000 obrażeń magicznych pochwyconym wrogom, odrzucając ich i ogłuszając na 1,5 sekundy.
skill.description_it: Fizz throws a lure that attracts a shark, causing it to emerge after a brief delay. It deals magic damage to enemies caught, knocking them back and stunning them for 1.5 seconds.

skill.name: Orbital Strike
skill.description: Gangplank calls down a large orbital strike around his target, dealing magic damage to all enemies in that area for 2 seconds.
skill.description_es: Ganplank ordena un ataque orbital alrededor de su objetivo, el cual inflige 650 de daño a todos los enemigos en una gran área después de 2 seg.
skill.description_pt: Gangplank chama um grande bombardeio cinético em volta de seu alvo, causando dano mágico a todos os inimigos naquela área por 2 segundos
skill.description_de: Gangplank beschwört einen heftigen Orbitalschlag herab, der nach 2 Sekunden Verzögerung allen Gegnern, die sich im Zielbereich befinden, Schaden zufügt.
skill.description_ru: Ганк планк вызывает большой орбитальный удар вокруг своей цели, нанося магический урон всем врагам в этой области в течение 2 секунд.
skill.description_ch: Gangplank calls down a large orbital strike around his target, dealing magic damage to all enemies in that area for 2 seconds.
skill.description_tr: Gangplank hedefi etrafında büyük bir yörünge saldırısı başlatır ve bu bölgedeki tüm düşmanlara 2 saniye boyunca büyü hasarı verir.
skill.description_vi: Gangplank triệu hồi vệ tinh tấn công mục tiêu của hắn, gây sát thương lên tất cả những kẻ địch trong phạm vi lớn trong 2 giây.
skill.description_fr: Gangplank lance une frappe orbitale sur sa cible, infligeant des dégâts à tous les ennemis dans la zone après 2 secondes.
skill.description_pl: Gangplank wzywa olbrzymi ostrzał z orbity dookoła wybranego celu. Zadaje on 650/850/9001 obrażeń magicznych wszystkim celom na tym obszarze w ciągu 2 sekund.
skill.description_it: Gangplank calls down a large orbital strike around his target, dealing magic damage to all enemies in that area for 2 seconds.

skill.name: Smoke Grenade
skill.description: Graves launches a smoke grenade toward the highest attack speed enemy, which explodes on impact dealing magic damage to enemies in the area and causing their attacks to miss.
skill.description_es: Graves lanza una granada de humo que se dirige al enemigo con mayor velocidad de ataque. La granada explota al impactar, inflige 150 de daño mágico a los enemigos cercanos y causaque sus ataques fallen.
skill.description_pt: Graves lança uma granada de fumaça em direção ao inimigo com a maior velocidade de ataque, explodindo ao impacto e causando dano mágico aos inimigos em área, fazendo-os errarem seus ataques.
skill.description_de: Graves schleudert eine Rauchgranate auf den Gegner mit dem höchsten Angriffstempo, die beim Aufprall explodiert. Gegner im Zielbereich erleiden  magischen Schaden und verfehlen ihre Ziele.
skill.description_ru: Graves launches a smoke grenade toward the highest attack speed enemy, which explodes on impact dealing magic damage to enemies in the area and causing their attacks to miss.
skill.description_ch: Graves launches a smoke grenade toward the highest attack speed enemy, which explodes on impact dealing magic damage to enemies in the area and causing their attacks to miss.
skill.description_tr: Graves saldırı hızı en yüksek olan düşmana bir sis bombası fırlatır. Patladığında büyü hasarı verir ve bölgede düşmanların boyunca saldırı kaçırmalarına sebep olur.
skill.description_vi: Graves bắn ra một quả đạn khói về phía đối thủ có Tốc độ Đánh cao nhất. Nó sẽ phát nổ khi chạm mục tiêu, gây sát thương phép lên tất cả kẻ địch trong vùng và khiến đòn đánh của chúng bị hụt.
skill.description_fr: Graves lance une grenade fumigène vers l\'ennemi qui a la vitesse d\'attaque la plus élevée, infligeant des dégâts aux ennemis dans la zone et empêchant leurs attaques de toucher pendant quelques secondes.
skill.description_pl: Graves rzuca granat dymny w kierunku wroga o najwyższej prędkości ataku. Granat wybucha przy trafieniu, zadając obrażeń magicznych wrogom na tym obszarze i sprawiając, że ich ataki pudłują.
skill.description_it: Graves launches a smoke grenade toward the highest attack speed enemy, which explodes on impact dealing magic damage to enemies in the area and causing their attacks to miss.

skill.name: Bladesurge
skill.description: Irelia dashes past her target, attacking them for a percentage of her Attack Damage as she passes through. If this kills the target, she casts again immediately at the enemy with the highest mana.
skill.description_es: Irelia se desplaza hacia su objetivo y realiza un ataque báscio que inflige 175% de su Daño de Ataque. Si esto mata a su objetivo, volverá a lanzar este hechizo de inmediato contra el enemigo que tenga más mana.
skill.description_pt: Irelia avança até seu alvo, usando um ataque básico com 175% de seu Dano de Ataque. Caso o alvo seja abtido, ela conjurará a habilidade mais uma vez imediatamente, focando o inimigo com a maior quantidade de mana.
skill.description_de: Irelia sprintet an ihrem Ziel vorbei und fügt ihm auf ihrem Weg einen Prozentteil ihres Angriffsschadens zu. Falls sie das Ziel dadurch tötet, aktiviert sie „Stürmende Klinge“ sofort ein zweites Mal und greift den Gegner mit dem höchsten Mana an.
skill.description_ru: Ирелия бросается мимо своей цели, нападая на них в процентах от ее урона от атаки, когда она проходит. Если это убивает цель, она снова немедленно бросает противнику самую высокую ману.
skill.description_ch: Irelia dashes past her target, attacking them for a percentage of her Attack Damage as she passes through. If this kills the target, she casts again immediately at the enemy with the highest mana.
skill.description_tr: Irelia dashes past her target, attacking them for a percentage of her Attack Damage as she passes through. If this kills the target, she casts again immediately at the enemy with the highest mana.
skill.description_vi: Irelia lướt xuyên qua mục tiêu, gây phần tram sát thương đòn đánh cơ bản lên nhưng tướng bị lướt qua. Nếu mục tiêu bị hạ gục, cô ngay lập tức sử dụng tiếp kĩ năng này lên mục tiêu có nhiều năng lượng nhất.
skill.description_fr: Irelia se rue à travers sa cible, lui infligeant des dégâts en fonction de son attaque. Si la cible meurt, Irelia relance son sort immédiatement sur l\'ennemi qui a le plus de mana.
skill.description_pl: Irelia doskakuje do celu i atakuje go, zadając 175%/250%/500% obrażeń od ataku. Jeśli w ten sposób zabije cel, natychmiast ponownie rzuca zaklęcie we wroga z najwyższą ilością many.
skill.description_it: Irelia dashes past her target, attacking them for a percentage of her Attack Damage as she passes through. If this kills the target, she casts again immediately at the enemy with the highest mana.

skill.name: Ageless Standard
skill.description: Jarvan calls down his standard to a nearby location, granting nearby allies Attack Speed for 6 seconds.
skill.description_es: Jarvan emplaza su estandarte en un lugar cercano, lo que otorga 60% de Velocidad de Ataque a todos los aliados cercanos durante 6 seg.
skill.description_pt: Jarvan invoca seu estandarte em um local próximo, concedendo a todos os aliados próximos 50% de Velocidade de Ataque por 6s.
skill.description_de: Jarvan ruft seine Standarte auf ein nahes Zielgebiet herab und gewährt dadurch allen nahen Verbündeten 6 Sekunden lang Angriffstempo.
skill.description_ru: Джарван вызывает свой стандарт к ближайшему месту, предоставляя ближайшим союзникам скорость атаки на 6 секунд.
skill.description_ch: Jarvan calls down his standard to a nearby location, granting nearby allies Attack Speed for 6 seconds.
skill.description_tr: Jarvan sancağını yakındaki bir yere çağırır ve yakındaki müttefiklere 6 saniye boyunca saldırı hızı verir.
skill.description_vi: Jarvan triệu hồi lá cờ của mình xuống một vị trí gần đó, tăng cho tất cả đồng minh xung quanh Tốc độ Đánh trong 6 giây.
skill.description_fr: Jarvan plante son étendard dans une zone proche, augmentant la vitesse d\'attaque des alliés proches.
skill.description_pl: Jarvan wbija chorągiew w pobliską lokację, dając wszystkim sojusznikom w jej otoczeniu 50/75/100% prędkości ataku na 6 sekund.
skill.description_it: Jarvan calls down his standard to a nearby location, granting nearby allies Attack Speed for 6 seconds.

skill.name: To the Skies
skill.description: Jayce jumps into the air and slams his hammer, dealing magic damage to nearby enemies.
skill.description_es: Jayce golpea con su martillo, lo que inflige 450 de daño mágico a los enemigos cercanos.
skill.description_pt: Jayce bate com seu martelo no chão, causando 450 de Dano Mágico aos inimigos próximos.
skill.description_de: Jayce springt in die Luft und schmettert seinen Hammer auf den Boden, wodurch nahe Gegner magischen Schaden erleiden.
skill.description_ru: Jayce jumps into the air and slams his hammer, dealing magic damage to nearby enemies.
skill.description_ch: Jayce jumps into the air and slams his hammer, dealing magic damage to nearby enemies.
skill.description_tr: Jayce havaya zıplar ve çekicini vurarak yakındaki düşmanlara büyü hasarı verir.
skill.description_vi: Jayce nhảy lên và nện búa, gây sát thương phép lên kẻ địch lân cận.
skill.description_fr: Jayce bondit et donne un coup de marteau, infligeant des dégâts aux ennemis proches.
skill.description_pl: Jayce wyskakuje i uderza swym młotem, zadając 450/600/1200 obrażeń magicznych pobliskim wrogom.
skill.description_it: Jayce jumps into the air and slams his hammer, dealing magic damage to nearby enemies.

skill.name: Whisper
skill.description: Jhin converts each 1% of bonus attack speed he has into 0.8 attack damage. Every fourth shot, Jhin deals a bonus percent of attack damage.
skill.description_es: Pasiva: Jhin convierte cada un 1% de Velocidad de Ataque adicional que posee en 0.8 de Daño de Ataque. Pasiva cada cuarto disparo, Jhin inflige un 244% de daño.
skill.description_pt: Passivo: Jhin converte cada 1% de Velocidade de Ataque adicional que tem em 0.8 de Dano de Ataque. Passivo: A cada quatro tiros, Jhin causa 244% de dano.
skill.description_de: Jhin wandelt jedes Prozent seines zusätzlichen Angriffstempos in 0,8 Angriffsschaden um. Bei jedem 4. Schuss verursacht Jhin einen zusätzlichen Prozentteil an Schaden.
skill.description_ru: Джин конвертирует каждый 1% бонусной скорости атаки в 0,8 урона от атаки. Каждый четвертый выстрел Джин наносит дополнительный процент урона от атаки.
skill.description_ch: Jhin converts each 1% of bonus attack speed he has into 0.8 attack damage. Every fourth shot, Jhin deals a bonus percent of attack damage.
skill.description_tr: Jhin converts each 1% of bonus attack speed he has into 0.8 attack damage. Every fourth shot, Jhin deals a bonus percent of attack damage.
skill.description_vi: Jhin chuyển hóa mỗi 1% tốc độ đánh cộng thêm thành 0.8 sát thương đòn đánh. Mỗi đòn đánh thứ 4, Jhin sẽ gây thêm phần trăm sát thương.
skill.description_fr: La vitesse d\'attaque supplémentaire de Jhin est convertie en dégâts d\'attaque. En outre, tous les quatres tirs, Jhin inflige des dégâts bonus.
skill.description_pl: Umiejętność bierna: Jhin przemienia każdy 1% swojej bonusowej prędkości ataku w 0,8 obrażeń od ataku. Co czwarty atak Jhina zadaje 244/344/444% obrażeń od ataku.
skill.description_it: Jhin converts each 1% of bonus attack speed he has into 0.8 attack damage. Every fourth shot, Jhin deals a bonus percent of attack damage.

skill.description_ru: Джин конвертирует каждый 1% бонусной скорости атаки в 0,8 урона от атаки. Каждый четвертый выстрел Джин наносит дополнительный процент урона от атаки.
skill.description_ch: Jhin converts each 1% of bonus attack speed he has into 0.8 attack damage. Every fourth shot, Jhin deals a bonus percent of attack damage.
skill.description_tr: Jhin converts each 1% of bonus attack speed he has into 0.8 attack damage. Every fourth shot, Jhin deals a bonus percent of attack damage.
skill.description_vi: Jhin chuyển hóa mỗi 1% tốc độ đánh cộng thêm thành 0.8 sát thương đòn đánh. Mỗi đòn đánh thứ 4, Jhin sẽ gây thêm phần trăm sát thương.
skill.description_fr: La vitesse d\'attaque supplémentaire de Jhin est convertie en dégâts d\'attaque. En outre, tous les quatres tirs, Jhin inflige des dégâts bonus.
skill.description_pl: Umiejętność bierna: Jhin przemienia każdy 1% swojej bonusowej prędkości ataku w 0,8 obrażeń od ataku. Co czwarty atak Jhina zadaje 244/344/444% obrażeń od ataku.
skill.description_it: Jhin converts each 1% of bonus attack speed he has into 0.8 attack damage. Every fourth shot, Jhin deals a bonus percent of attack damage.

skill.name: Get Excited
skill.description: Jinx gets excited as she helps take down enemies. After her first takedown, Jinx gains bonus attack speed. After her second takedown, Jinx swaps to her rocket launcher, causing her Basic Attacks to deal bonus magic damage to all enemies in a small area around her target.
skill.description_es: Pasiva: Jinx comienza a emocionarse conforme ayuda a derribar unidades enemigas. Tras su primer derribo, Jinx obtiene 60% de Velocidad de Ataque adicional. Luego de su segundo derribo, Jinx empieza a atacar con su lanzacohetes, con el cual sus ataques básicos ahora infligen 100 de daño mágico adicional a todos los enemigos en un área reducida al rededor del objetivo.
skill.description_pt: Passivo: Jinx fica animada ao ajudar no abate de unidades inimigas! Depois de sua primeira eliminação, ela recebe 60% de Velocidade  de Ataque adicional. Depois da segunda eliminação, ela troca para o lança-mísseis, fazendo com que seus ataques básicos causem 100 de Dano Mágico adicional a todos os inimigos em uma pequena área ao redor do alvo.
skill.description_de: Jinx dreht richtig auf, wenn sie hilft, gegnerische Einheiten auszuschalten. Nachdem sie das erste Mal an einem Kill beteiligt ist, erhält Jinx zusätzliches Angriffstempo. Nach dem zweiten erledigten Gegner wechselt sie zu ihrem Raketenwerfer und fügt allen Gegnern in einem kleinen Bereich um ihr Ziel mit ihren normalen Angriffen zusätzlichen magischen Schaden zu.
skill.description_ru: Jinx возбуждается, когда она помогает победить врагов. После первого удара Джинкс получает бонусную скорость атаки. После второго удара Джинкс переключается на свою ракетную установку, в результате чего ее базовые атаки наносят дополнительный магический урон всем врагам в небольшой области вокруг ее цели.
skill.description_ch: Jinx gets excited as she helps take down enemies. After her first takedown, Jinx gains bonus attack speed. After her second takedown, Jinx swaps to her rocket launcher, causing her Basic Attacks to deal bonus magic damage to all enemies in a small area around her target.
skill.description_tr: Jinx, düşmanları öldürmeye yardım ettiğinde heyecanlanır. İlk öldürmeden sonra Jinx ilave saldırı hızı kazanır. İkinci öldürmeden sonra Jinx, roketatarını değiştirir ve temel saldırıları hedefinin etrafındaki küçük bir alandaki tüm düşmanlara fazladan büyü hasarı vermesine neden olur.
skill.description_vi: Jinx đạt trạng thái hưng phấn sau khi tham gia hạ gục đối thủ. Sau mạng tham gia hạ gục đầu tiên, Jinx nhận thêm Tốc độ Đánh. Sau mạng thứ hai, Jinx đổi sang súng phóng lựu, khiến đòn đánh thường của cô gây thêm sát thương phép lên một vùng nhỏ xung quanh mục tiêu.
skill.description_fr: Après une élimination, Jinx gagne de la vitesse d\'attaque. Après la deuxième, ses attaques infligent des dégâts de zone autour de sa cible.
skill.description_pl: Umiejętność bierna: Jinx ekscytuje się udziałami w zabójstwach. Po pierwszym udziale w zabójstwie Jinx zdobywa 60/75/100% bonusowej szybkości ataku. Po drugim udziale w zabójstwie Jinx przerzuca się na swoją wyrzutnię rakiet, dzięki czemu jej ataki podstawowe zadają 100/175/750 premiowych obrażeń magicznych wszystkim wrogom w niewielkiej odległości od jej celu.
skill.description_it: Jinx gets excited as she helps take down enemies. After her first takedown, Jinx gains bonus attack speed. After her second takedown, Jinx swaps to her rocket launcher, causing her Basic Attacks to deal bonus magic damage to all enemies in a small area around her target.

skill.name: Missile Rain
skill.description: Kai\'Sa launches missiles towards each nearby enemy that deal 50 magic damage each.
skill.description_es: Kai\'Sa lanza 4 misiles hacia cada enemigo cercano que infligen 50 daño mágico
skill.description_pt: Kai\'sa dispara 4 mísseis na direção de cada inimigo próximo, causando 50 de Dano Mágico.
skill.description_de: Kai\'Sa feuert Geschosse auf jeden nahen Gegner ab, von denen jedes 50 magischen Schaden verursacht.
skill.description_ru: Kai\'Sa запускает ракеты в направлении каждого находящегося поблизости противника, которые наносят 50 магического урона каждая.
skill.description_ch: Kai\'Sa launches missiles towards each nearby enemy that deal 50 magic damage each.
skill.description_tr: Kai\'Sa, yakındaki her düşmana 50 büyü hasarı veren füzeler fırlatır.
skill.description_vi: Kai\'Sa phóng ra hỏa tiễn về phía các mục tiêu lân cận, gây 50 sát thương phép với mỗi tên lửa.
skill.description_fr: Kai\'Sa envoie plusieurs missiles vers les adversaires à proximité, leur infligeant des dégâts.
skill.description_pl: Kai’Sa wystrzeliwuje 6/8/11 pocisków w kierunku każdego pobliskiego wroga. Każdy pocisk zadaje 50 obrażeń magicznych.
skill.description_it: Kai\'Sa launches missiles towards each nearby enemy that deal 50 magic damage each.

skill.name: Inspire
skill.description: At the start of combat, Karma tethers to her closest ally. Karma shields the tethered ally, or random if the ally is dead for 4 seconds. While the shield holds, the ally receives bonus attack speed.
skill.description_es: Al inicio del combate, Karma crea una conexión con su aliado más cercano. Karma otorga un escudo de 250 de Vida al aliado con el que se conectó (o a uno aleatorio si este muere) durante 4 seg. Mientras el escudo esté activo, el aliado recibirá 35% de Velocidad de Ataque adicional
skill.description_pt: No início de combate Karma se conecta ao aliado mais próximo. Ela concede ao aliado conectado (ou a um aliado aleatório, caso o aliado protegido tenha morrido) um escudo de 250 de Vida por 4s. enquanto o escfudo estiver ativo, o aliado recebe 35% de Velocidade de Ataque adicional.
skill.description_de: Karma verbindet sich zu Kampfbeginn mit dem nächstgelegenen Verbündete. Karma gewährt ihm (oder einem zufälligen Verbündeten, falls die Verbindung getrennt wurde) 4 Sekunden lang einen Schild, der  Schaden absorbiert. Solange der Schild aktiv ist, erhöht sich das Angriffstempo des Verbündeten zusätzlich.
skill.description_ru: В начале боя Карма привязывает своего ближайшего союзника. Карма защищает привязанного союзника, или случайный, если союзник мертв в течение 4 секунд. Пока щит держится, союзник получает бонус скорости атаки.
skill.description_ch: At the start of combat, Karma tethers to her closest ally. Karma shields the tethered ally, or random if the ally is dead for 4 seconds. While the shield holds, the ally receives bonus attack speed.
skill.description_tr: Çatışmanın başlangıcında Karma, en yakın müttefikiyle bağlanır.  Karma, bağlı müttefike kalkan verir eğer müttefik ölürse rastgele başka bir müttefike verir. Kalkan olduğu sürece müttefik ilave saldırı hızı kazanır.
skill.description_vi: Khi bắt đầu trận, Karma liên kết với đồng minh gần nhất. Karma tạo lá chắn cho đồng minh liên kết (hoặc đồng minh ngẫu nhiên nếu đồng minh liên kết bị hạ gục) trong 4 giây. Khi lá chắn còn tồn tại, đồng minh được tăng thêm tốc độ đánh.
skill.description_fr: Au début du combat, Karma se lie avec l\'allié le plus proche. Elle lui donne un bouclier et de la vitesse d\'attaque supplémentaire.
skill.description_pl: Na początku walki Karma łączy się z najbliższym sojusznikiem i osłania go tarczą o wartości 250/400/800 na 4 sekundy (lub losowego sojusznika, jeśli połączony sojusznik jest martwy). W trakcie trwania tarczy sojusznik otrzymuje 35/50/100% bonusowej prędkości ataku.
skill.description_it: At the start of combat, Karma tethers to her closest ally. Karma shields the tethered ally, or random if the ally is dead for 4 seconds. While the shield holds, the ally receives bonus attack speed.

skill.name: Force Pulse
skill.description: Kassadin releases a wave of energy in front of him, dealing magic damage and disarming all targets hit.
skill.description_es: Kassadin emite una onda de energia frente a él que inflige 250 de daño mágico y desarma a todos los enemigos afectados durante 2.5 seg.
skill.description_pt: Kassadin lança uma onde de energia à sua frente, causando 250 de Dano Mágico e desarmando todos o alvos atingidos por 2.5s.
skill.description_de: Kassadin entfesselt in einem Bereich vor sich eine Energiewelle, die allen getroffenen Zielen magischen Schaden zufügt und sie entwaffnet.
skill.description_ru: Кассадин выпускает волну энергии перед собой, нанося магический урон и разоружая все пораженные цели.
skill.description_ch: Kassadin releases a wave of energy in front of him, dealing magic damage and disarming all targets hit.
skill.description_tr: Kassadin releases a wave of energy in front of him, dealing magic damage and disarming all targets hit.
skill.description_vi: Kassadin giải phóng một đợt sóng năng lượng ra trước mặt, gây sát thương phép và giải giới tất cả mục tiêu trúng chiêu.
skill.description_fr: Kassadin projette uen vague d\'énergie devant lui, infligeant des dégâts et désarmant les adversaires touchés.
skill.description_pl: Kassadin uwalnia przed sobą falę energii, zadając 300/450/900 obrażeń magicznych i rozbrajając wszystkie trafione cele na 2,5/3/3,5 sekundy.
skill.description_it: Kassadin releases a wave of energy in front of him, dealing magic damage and disarming all targets hit.

skill.name: Ascent

skill.description_pt: Kayle ascende, fazendo com que seus ataques emitam ondas que causam 125 de Dano Mágico adcional.
skill.description_de: Kayle steigt auf, wodurch ihre Angriffe bis zum Ende des Kampfs Wellen auslösen, die zusätzlichen magischen Schaden verursachen.
skill.description_ru: Кейл поднимается, заставляя ее атаки запускать волны, которые наносят дополнительный магический урон до конца боя.
skill.description_ch: Kayle Ascends, causing her attacks to launch waves that deal bonus magic damage until the end of combat.
skill.description_tr: Kayle Yükselir ve saldırılarının savaşın sonuna kadar ilave büyü hasarı veren dalgalar fırlatmasına neden olur.
skill.description_vi: Kayle Đột Phá, khiến những đòn đánh của bản thân phóng ra sóng lửa, gây thêm sát thương phép.
skill.description_fr: Les attaques de base de Kayle infligent des vagues de dégâts magiques en zone jusqu\'à la fin du combat.
skill.description_pl: Kayle zostaje Wyniesiona, co sprawia, że jej ataki wyzwalają fale zadające 125/200/750 bonusowych obrażeń magicznych do końca walki.
skill.description_it: Kayle Ascends, causing her attacks to launch waves that deal bonus magic damage until the end of combat.

skill.name: Taste their Fear
skill.description: Kha\'Zix slashes the nearest enemy, dealing magic damage. If the target has no adjacent teammates, this damage is increased.
skill.description_es: Kha\'Zix corta al enemigo más cercano e inflige 175 de daño mágico. Si el enemigo no tiene aliados adyacentes, el daño aumentará a 525
skill.description_pt: Kha\'Zix corta o inimigo mais próximo, causando 175 de Dano Mágico. Se o inimigo não tiver aliados adjacentes, o dano é aumentado para 525.
skill.description_de: Kha\'Zix attackiert den nächstgelegenen Gegner und fügt ihm magischen Schaden zu. Wenn sich keine anderen Gegner neben dem Ziel befinden, wird der Schaden erhöht.
skill.description_ru: Казикс наносит удар ближайшему врагу, нанося магический урон. Если у цели нет соседних товарищей по команде, этот урон увеличивается.
skill.description_ch: Kha\'Zix slashes the nearest enemy, dealing magic damage. If the target has no adjacent teammates, this damage is increased.
skill.description_tr: Kha\'Zix, en yakın düşmanı keserek büyü hasarı verir.Eğer hedefin bitişiğinde takım arkadaşları yoksa, bu hasar artar.
skill.description_vi: Kha\'Zix tấn công mục tiêu gần nhất, gây sát thương phép. Nếu mục tiêu không có đồng đội đứng cạnh, sát thương được tăng lên.
skill.description_fr: Kha\'Zix découpe l\'adversaire le plus proche, lui infligeant des dégâts. Il inflige des dégâts supplémentaires s\'il est isolé.
skill.description_pl: Kha’Zix przecina najbliższego wroga, zadając mu 200/250/350 obrażeń magicznych. Jeżeli w pobliżu celu nie znajdują się jego sojusznicy, obrażenia są zwiększone do 600/750/1050.
skill.description_it: Kha\'Zix slashes the nearest enemy, dealing magic damage. If the target has no adjacent teammates, this damage is increased.

skill.name: Cyber Barrier

skill.description_es: Leona crea una barrera, reduciendo el daño que le proporcionan por 4 segundos.
skill.description_pt: Leona cria uma barreira, reduzindo todo o dano iminente por 4 segundos
skill.description_de: Leona erschafft eine Barriere, die 4 Sekunden lang jeglichen erlittenen Schaden verringert.
skill.description_ru: Леона создает барьер, уменьшая весь входящий урон на 4 секунды.
skill.description_ch: Leona creates a barrier, reducing all incoming damage for 4 seconds.
skill.description_tr: Leona bir bariyer yaratarak gelen tüm hasarı 4 saniye boyunca azaltır.
skill.description_vi: Leona tạo ra một lớp lá chắn, giảm thiểu tất cả sát thương nhận vào đi trong vòng 4 giây.
skill.description_fr: Leona crée une barrière qui bloque des dégâts pendant 4 secondes.
skill.description_pl: Leona tworzy barierę redukującą wszystkie nadchodzące obrażenia o 40/80/120 przez 4 sekundy.
skill.description_it: Leona creates a barrier, reducing all incoming damage for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Relentless Pursuit
skill.description: Lucian dashes away from his current target, then Basic Attacks them and fires a second shot which deals magic damage.
skill.description_es: Lucian se aleja de su objetivo actual, luego realiza un ataque básico y lanza un segundo disparo, lo cual inflige 150 de daño mágico.
skill.description_pt: Lucian avança para longe do seu alvo atual, depois o atinge com um ataque básico e um segundo tiro que cause 150 de Dano Mágico.
skill.description_de: Lucian sprintet von seinem derzeitigen Ziel weg, greift es dann normal an und feuert einen zweiten Schuss ab, der magischen Schaden verursacht.
skill.description_ru: Люциан бросается прочь от своей текущей цели, затем Базово атакует их и делает второй выстрел, который наносит магический урон.
skill.description_ch: Lucian dashes away from his current target, then Basic Attacks them and fires a second shot which deals magic damage.
skill.description_tr: Lucian dashes away from his current target, then Basic Attacks them and fires a second shot which deals magic damage.
skill.description_vi: Lucian lướt ra xa khỏi mục tiêu hiện tại, sau đó tung đòn đánh cơ bản kèm theo một đòn đánh thứ hai gây sát thương phép.
skill.description_fr: Lucian s\'éloigne de sa cible actuelle, puis l\'attaque en infligeant des dégâts bonus.
skill.description_pl: Lucian wykonuje odskok z dala od aktualnego celu, następnie wymierza w niego atak podstawowy i oddaje drugi strzał, który zadaje 175/225/350 obrażeń magicznych.
skill.description_it: Lucian dashes away from his current target, then Basic Attacks them and fires a second shot which deals magic damage.

skill.name: Mass Polymorph
skill.description: Lulu polymorphs the nearest enemies for 4 seconds, rendering them unable to attack or cast, and causing them to hop around aimlessly. Polymorphed enemies take additional damage.
skill.description_es: Lulu aplica poliformia a los 2 enemigos más cercanos durante 3 seg, lo que les impide atacar o lanzar hechizos y hace que salten una y otra vez sin rumbo. Los enemigos bajo el efecto de poliformia reciben 5% de daño adicional de todas las fuentes.
skill.description_pt: Lulu polymorphs the nearest enemies for 4 seconds, rendering them unable to attack or cast, and causing them to hop around aimlessly. Polymorphed enemies take additional damage.
skill.description_de: Lulu verwandelt die nächstgelegenen Gegner, die dann 4 Sekunden lang weder angreifen noch Fähigkeiten aktivieren können und stattdessen ziellos herumhüpfen. Verwandelte Gegner erleiden zusätzlichen Schaden.
skill.description_ru: Лулу полиморфирует ближайших врагов на 4 секунды, делая их неспособными атаковать или сотворять, и заставляя их бесцельно прыгать. Полиморфные враги получают дополнительный урон.
skill.description_ch: Lulu polymorphs the nearest enemies for 4 seconds, rendering them unable to attack or cast, and causing them to hop around aimlessly. Polymorphed enemies take additional damage.
skill.description_tr: Lulu, en yakın düşmanları 4 saniyeliğine polimorfize ederek saldıramaz hale getirir ve amaçsızca zıplamalarına neden olur. Polimorfik düşmanlar ek hasar alır.
skill.description_vi: Lulu biến thú kẻ địch gần nhất trong 4 giây, khiến chúng di chuyển bất định và không thể tấn công hay dùng kĩ năng. Tướng bị biến thú chịu thêm sát thương.
skill.description_fr: Lulu transforme les ennemis les plus proches en plusieurs secondes, les empêchant d\'attaquer ou de lancer des sorts et les faisant sautiller de façon aléatoire. Les ennemis transformés subissent des dégâts supplémentaires.
skill.description_pl: Lulu nakłada efekt polimorfii na 2/3/12 najbliższych wrogów na 3/3/8 sekund, sprawiając, że nie mogą oni atakować ani rzucać zaklęć. Otrzymują oni 5/10/25% dodatkowych obrażeń.
skill.description_it: Lulu polymorphs the nearest enemies for 4 seconds, rendering them unable to attack or cast, and causing them to hop around aimlessly. Polymorphed enemies take additional damage.

skill.name: Lurid Binding
skill.description: Lux fires a sphere of darkness towards the farthest enemy. Enemies caught along its path take magic damage and are stunned.
skill.description_es: Lux lanza una esfera de oscuridad hacia el enemigo más lejano. Los enemigos en su trayectoria reciben 200 de daño mágico y quedan aturdidos durante 1.5 seg.
skill.description_pt: Lux fires a sphere of darkness towards the farthest enemy. Enemies caught along its path take magic damage and are stunned.
skill.description_de: Lux entfesselt eine Sphäre der Finsternis in Richtung des am weitesten entfernten Gegners. Gegner, die auf dem Flug der Sphäre getroffen werden, erleiden magischen Schaden und werden betäubt.
skill.description_ru: Люкс обстреливает сферу тьмы по отношению к самому дальнему врагу. Враги, пойманные на его пути, получают магический урон и оглушаются.
skill.description_ch: Lux fires a sphere of darkness towards the farthest enemy. Enemies caught along its path take magic damage and are stunned.
skill.description_tr: Lux, en uzak düşmana doğru bir karanlık küresi fırlatır. Yol boyunca yakalanan düşmanlar büyü hasarı alır ve sersemler.
skill.description_vi: Lux bắn một quả cầu năng lượng hắc ám đến kẻ địch ở xa nhất. Mục tiêu nằm trên đường bay chịu sát thương phép và bị làm choáng.
skill.description_fr: Lux tire une sphère de ténèbres qui traverse les ennemis, leur infligeant des dégâts et les étourdissants.
skill.description_pl: Lux wystrzeliwuje sferę ciemności, która przenika przez wrogów, zadając im 200/300/600 obrażeń magicznych i ogłuszając ich na 1,5/2/2,5 sekundy.
skill.description_it: Lux fires a sphere of darkness towards the farthest enemy. Enemies caught along its path take magic damage and are stunned.

skill.name: Energy Shield

skill.description_pt: Passivo: Malphite inicia o combate com um escudo igual a 40% de sua Vida máxima.
skill.description_de: Malphite beginnt den Kampf mit einem Schild in Höhe von Prozentteil seines maximalen Lebens.
skill.description_ru: Мальфит начинает бой со щитом, равным проценту от его максимального здоровья.
skill.description_ch: Malphite starts combat with a shield equal to a percent of his maximum health.
skill.description_tr: Malphite maksimum sağlığının yüzde birine eşit bir kalkanla savaşa başlar.
skill.description_vi: Malphite bắt đầu trận chiến với một lá chắn tương đương với phần trăm máu tối đa.

skill.name: Chosen One

skill.description_ch: For 5 seconds, Master Yi gains massively increased movement speed, heals for a percentage of his maximum health each second, and deals bonus true damage with his Basic Attacks.

skill.description_fr: Maître Yi gagne des dégâts bruts bonus à l\'impact pendant quelques secondes et se soigne d\'une partie de ses dégâts.
skill.description_pl: Na 5 sekund Master Yi otrzymuje olbrzymi bonus prędkości ruchu, uzdrawia się o 8/10/15% swojego maksymalnego zdrowia na sekundę i zadaje 75/100/200 bonusowych nieuchronnych obrażeń za pomocą ataków podstawowych.
skill.description_it: For 5 seconds, Master Yi gains massively increased movement speed, heals for a percentage of his maximum health each second, and deals bonus true damage with his Basic Attacks.

skill.description: Miss Fortune channels and fires waves of bullets in a cone for 2.25 seconds, dealing a percentage of enemies\' maximum health in magic damage over the duration.
skill.description_es: Miss Fortune canaliza y dispara varias oleadas de balas en un cono durante 2.25 seg, lo que inflige 70% de la Vida Máxima de los enemigos como daño mágico a lo largo de su duración.
skill.description_pt: Miss Fortune channels and fires waves of bullets in a cone for 2.25 seconds, dealing a percentage of enemies\' maximum health in magic damage over the duration.
skill.description_de: Miss Fortune kanalisiert und feuert 2,25 Sekunden lang Kugelsalven in einem kegelförmigen Bereich ab. Währenddessen fügt sie ihren Gegnern einen Prozentteil ihres maximalen Lebens als magischen Schaden zu.

skill.description_ch: Miss Fortune channels and fires waves of bullets in a cone for 2.25 seconds, dealing a percentage of enemies\' maximum health in magic damage over the duration.

skill.description_it: Miss Fortune channels and fires waves of bullets in a cone for 2.25 seconds, dealing a percentage of enemies\' maximum health in magic damage over the duration.

skill.name: Pop Blossom

skill.description_ch: Neeko leaps into the air and slams into the ground, dealing magic damage and stunning all nearby enemies.

skill.description_it: Neeko leaps into the air and slams into the ground, dealing magic damage and stunning all nearby enemies.

skill.name: Buckler Toss
skill.description: Poppy throws her buckler at the furthest enemy dealing damage. The buckler bounces back to Poppy, shielding her.
skill.description_es: Poppy lanza su escudo al enemigo más lejano e inflige 100 de daño. El escudo rebota, y protege a Poppy conta 200 de daño.
skill.description_pt: Poppy arremessa seu escudo no inimigo mais distante, causando 100 de dano. O escudo ricocheteia de volta para Poppy, protegendo-a contra 200 de dano.
skill.description_de: Poppy schleudert ihren Faustschild auf den am weitesten entfernten Gegner und fügt ihm Schaden zu. Dann springt der Faustschild zu Poppy zurück und schirmt sie gegen Schaden ab.
skill.description_ru: Поппи бросает свой баклер в дальний враг, наносящий урон. Баклер отскакивает к Поппи, прикрывая ее.
skill.description_ch: Poppy throws her buckler at the furthest enemy dealing damage. The buckler bounces back to Poppy, shielding her.
skill.description_tr: Poppy throws her buckler at the furthest enemy dealing damage. The buckler bounces back to Poppy, shielding her.
skill.description_vi: Rakan lướt đến rồi nhảy lên không trung, hất tung và gây sát thương phép lên kẻ địch xung quanh.
skill.description_fr: Poppy jette son bouclier sur l\'ennemi le plus éloigné, lui infligeant des dégâts. Le bouclier revient ensuite sur Poppy pour lui donner un bouclier.
skill.description_pl: Poppy rzuca swoim puklerzem w najdalszego wroga, zadając mu 100/175/250 obrażeń. Puklerz odbija się i wraca do Poppy, osłaniając ją tarczą o wartości 200/300/400.

skill.name: Grand Entrance
skill.description: Rakan dashes to the furthest enemy within range and leaps into the air, knocking up and dealing magic damage to all nearby enemies.
skill.description_es: Rakan se desplaza hacia su objetivo y da un salto que lanza por el aire a todos los enemigos cercanos, lo que inflige 175 de daño mágico
skill.description_pt: Rakan avança até o alvo e salta, arremessando os inimigos próximos ao ar causando 175 de Dano Mágico.
skill.description_de: Rakan sprintet zu seinem Ziel und springt dann in die Luft. Dabei werden alle nahen Gegner hochgeschleudert und erleiden magischen Schaden.
skill.description_ru: Ракан бросается к своей цели атаки и прыгает в воздух, подбрасывая и нанося магический урон всем находящимся поблизости противникам.

skill.description_tr: Rakan dashes to his attack target and leaps into the air, knocking up and dealing magic damage to all nearby enemies.

skill.description_tr: Rumble torches his enemies, dealing magic damage in a cone over 3 seconds, and reducing healing on them by 50% for 5 seconds.

skill.description_fr: Rumble brûle ses ennemis, infligeant des dégâts en cône sur quelques secondes et réduisant leurs soins.

skill.name: Deceive

skill.description_pt: Shaco se teleportae apunhala o alvo pelas costas, causando 250% de dano de ataque básico. Essegolpe sempre será um Acerto Crítico.

skill.description_ch: Shaco teleports and backstabs his target, critically striking for a percentage of his Basic Attack damage.

skill.description_fr: Shaco se téléporte vers un adversaire et lui inflgie un coup dans le dos. Ce coup inflige un critique en fonction de ses dégâts de base.

skill.name: Assault and Battery

skill.description_es: Vi carga hacia el enemigo más lejano y lanza hacia un lado a todos los enemigos en el camino, lo que inflige 150 de daño mágico. Cuando alcanza a su objetivo, lo lanza por el aire durante 2 seg y le inflige 400 de daño mágico.
skill.description_pt: Vi avança até o inimigo mais distante, arremessando para o lado todos em seu caminho e causando 150 de Dano Mágico. Quando chega ao seu alvo, ela o arremessa ao ar por 2s e causa 400 de Dano Mágico

skill.description_ch: Vi charges at the furthest enemy, knocking aside and dealing magic damage to all enemies along the way. When she reaches her target, she deals magic damage and knocks them up.

skill.description_it: Vi charges at the furthest enemy, knocking aside and dealing magic damage to all enemies along the way. When she reaches her target, she deals magic damage and knocks them up.
